Cable Wireless Plc CAWL.L> merge Hong Kong Telephone Co Ltd TELH.HK> Cable Wireless (Hong Kong) Ltd> unit hold firm call Hong Kong Telecommunications Ltd>. Under merger H.K. Telephone shareholder receive H.K. Telecommunication share par value 50 H.K. Cents H.K. Telephone share par dlr. H.K. Telephone shareholder Cable Wireless receive warrant one-for-five basis entitle acquire Cable Wireless Plc five H.K. Telecom share 10 dlrs each. The Cable Wireless Plc hold 70 pct H.K. Telephone. It own 80 pct Cable Wireless (Hong Kong) Hong Kong government hold balance. Trading H.K. Telephone share suspend October 15. The share trade 19.30 dlrs. REUTER 